Too early?

00:02:35.630 --> 00:02:36.870
You're late.

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.030
Watch and learn.

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.020
I am Chi Yun,

00:02:41.310 --> 00:02:42.770
Chief of Huoyun Fortress.

00:02:42.810 --> 00:02:44.750
I've come to pay my respects
to Sword King Yu.

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:45.420
However,

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:46.400
I left in a hurry and forgot

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:47.730
to bring my invitation.

00:02:49.310 --> 00:02:50.520
Please,

00:02:51.079 --> 00:02:51.810
do us a favor.

00:02:53.340 --> 00:02:54.310
Huoyun Fortress?

00:02:54.310 --> 00:02:55.310
Never heard of it!

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:56.360
Some no-name sect

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:57.240
trying to freeload

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.280
in Sword King City?

00:02:58.280 --> 00:02:58.810
Get lost!

00:02:59.710 --> 00:03:00.360
Chi Yun,

00:03:00.630 --> 00:03:02.030
it seems Sword King City

00:03:02.350 --> 00:03:04.400
doesn't care much for your reputation

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:05.360
as the Cloud.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:07.870
Foxy Tang,

00:03:08.520 --> 00:03:10.000
how big a scene should I make?

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.840
That depends on how capable

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:12.840
you are.

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:20.750
No private fights

00:03:20.750 --> 00:03:21.810
in Sword King City!

00:03:34.190 --> 00:03:34.850
Commander,

00:03:35.150 --> 00:03:38.410
they're trying to force their way in
without invitations.

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.030
During the Sword Duel Festival,

00:03:41.030 --> 00:03:42.400
no one enters
the city

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.600
without an invitation,

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:44.950
not even the Cloud.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:46.960
I heard that

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:50.400
the Sword Duel Festival welcomes
heroes from all over the world.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:51.700
But now it seems there is

00:03:51.700 --> 00:03:53.300
a clear hierarchy after all.

00:03:55.310 --> 00:03:56.640
Go get your punishment.

00:03:56.870 --> 00:03:57.190
Yes.

00:03:57.790 --> 00:03:58.990
He acted recklessly.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:00.560
Please forgive him.

00:04:01.330 --> 00:04:03.790
However, this is the rule
of Sword King City.

00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:05.640
If you don't have invitations,

00:04:06.150 --> 00:04:06.750
I'm afraid

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:08.460
I cannot let you in.

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:13.630
What if I

00:04:14.190 --> 00:04:15.950
insist on entering today?

00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:27.970
Wanqiao Chamber is entering!

00:04:28.190 --> 00:04:30.560
Clear the way!

00:04:44.950 --> 00:04:46.630
Wanqiao Chamber is entering!

00:04:46.630 --> 00:04:49.240
Clear the way!

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:07.160
The Master of Wanqiao Chamber

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:08.750
congratulates the Yu family
on the festival

00:05:08.750 --> 00:05:10.310
and presents 10 baskets of pearls.

00:05:10.310 --> 00:05:11.680
During the festival,

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:13.390
