00:05:13.390 --> 00:05:14.600
are on the house.

00:05:20.830 --> 00:05:22.000
What a show-off.

00:05:29.800 --> 00:05:31.630
Wanqiao Chamber's treasure ship
has arrived.

00:05:31.630 --> 00:05:32.510
Sir, I think

00:05:32.970 --> 00:05:34.630
you should step aside for now.

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:36.500
The winds are high,
and the waves are rough.

00:05:36.500 --> 00:05:37.830
Perfect for traveling.

00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:39.130
Your small boat is packed with people.

00:05:39.130 --> 00:05:40.330
Beware of capsizing.

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:47.120
Watch out!

00:05:47.270 --> 00:05:48.530
You're about to crash!

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:50.360
Stop!

00:05:57.190 --> 00:05:58.600
Greetings, Master.

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:05.050
You're the Master of Wanqiao Chamber?

00:06:08.750 --> 00:06:09.390
Well,

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:10.800
since I can't enter Sword King City

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:12.040
as Tang Lici,

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:14.390
then I'll just have to

00:06:14.390 --> 00:06:15.510
borrow the invitation

00:06:15.510 --> 00:06:16.640
of Wanqiao Chamber.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:17.600
Just now,

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:20.680
I didn't know
you were the Master of Wanqiao Chamber.

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:22.010
I may have offended you.

00:06:22.270 --> 00:06:23.000
I apologize.

00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:25.320
But I don't understand.

00:06:25.870 --> 00:06:28.200
Why would you, with an invitation in hand,

00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:30.070
still make such a big scene?

00:06:30.130 --> 00:06:31.600
If I hadn't made a scene,

00:06:32.430 --> 00:06:33.480
how else could I see

00:06:33.480 --> 00:06:34.810
where the problem lies?

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:38.260
Commander,

00:06:38.450 --> 00:06:39.120
have we just offended

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.630
the Master of Wanqiao Chamber?

00:06:40.630 --> 00:06:41.760
Go tell Sword King Yu

00:06:42.409 --> 00:06:44.800
that I'm eccentric by nature

00:06:45.370 --> 00:06:46.700
and dislike being seen,

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.930
so there's no need to blame anyone.

00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:54.390
Guys,

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.050
please get on board.

00:06:59.230 --> 00:07:00.670
He's showing off again.

00:07:24.500 --> 00:07:25.370
Foxy Tang,

00:07:25.830 --> 00:07:27.240
this is

00:07:27.240 --> 00:07:28.360
way too…

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:33.400
luxurious.

00:07:35.370 --> 00:07:36.300
H-How much money

00:07:36.330 --> 00:07:37.480
do you actually have?

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:38.210
I don't know.

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:39.360
Never counted it.

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:41.800
I remember you were never

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:43.200
interested in business.

00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:45.670
What's your plan for running

00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:47.190
Wanqiao Chamber?

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:48.440
Does one have to live

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:50.610
only for what one's interested in?

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:52.090
Tang Sen.

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:54.480
Yes.

00:07:54.930 --> 00:07:56.530
Help my friends settle in.

00:07:57.090 --> 00:07:58.200
Make sure they feel

00:07:58.890 --> 00:08:00.040
right at home.

00:08:00.760 --> 00:08:01.490
Yes, Master.

00:08:13.510 --> 00:08:14.480
This young man's talent

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:15.340
is impressive.

00:08:15.630 --> 00:08:16.600
He's lasted 30 minutes

00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:17.950
against Sword King Yu.

00:08:18.200 --> 00:08:19.250
Impressive!

00:08:27.070 --> 00:08:28.070
The Sword King is formidable!

00:08:28.070 --> 00:08:29.000
You're too kind.

00:08:34.270 --> 00:08:35.730
You have great potential.

00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:37.960
Work hard, and you will

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:39.500
achieve great things.

00:08:41.570 --> 00:08:42.230
Look at him.

00:08:42.510 --> 00:08:43.990
The Sword King gave him personal pointers,

00:08:43.990 --> 00:08:45.800
yet he just walked away without a word.

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:46.710
How rude.

00:08:46.730 --> 00:08:47.890
What's talent worth

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:50.060
if you don't have manners?

00:08:50.280 --> 00:08:51.610
Zhong, did you see that?

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:53.150
Sword King Yu just aimed for

00:08:53.150 --> 00:08:54.080
his vital point.

00:08:54.380 --> 00:08:56.660
And his angle was extremely tricky.

00:08:57.510 --> 00:08:58.670
Good thing we had a clear view

00:08:58.670 --> 00:08:59.320
from here.

00:09:00.710 --> 00:09:01.870
If Mr. Lin hadn't

00:09:01.870 --> 00:09:03.330
dodged at the last second,

00:09:04.140 --> 00:09:05.140
he'd be crippled—

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:06.360
if not dead.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.290
The path of martial arts runs deep.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:11.490
Talent is like a small boat.

00:09:12.060 --> 00:09:13.730
It can carry you or sink you.

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:15.120
One can't

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:16.920
rely solely on talent

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.180
and lose humility.

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:19.390
There are

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:21.390
no shortcuts.

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:22.440
But why did Sword King Yu

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:23.840
go that hard on him?

00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:27.270
Perhaps out of jealousy.

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:30.270
Exactly.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:32.930
Does anyone else

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:35.730
wish to come up and compete?

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:31.580
Master,

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:33.320
here is the account book
for the six months

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:34.320
you've been away.

00:10:39.750 --> 00:10:41.480
Any word from my foster father?

00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:42.740
The imperial father-in-law says

00:10:42.740 --> 00:10:43.970
everything in Wanqiao Chamber

00:10:43.970 --> 00:10:45.100
is at your disposal.

00:10:50.870 --> 00:10:51.470
By the way,

00:10:52.390 --> 00:10:53.120
Miss Shei

00:10:53.790 --> 00:10:55.720
seems interested in bookkeeping.

00:10:56.530 --> 00:10:57.250
Got it.

00:11:10.710 --> 00:11:11.400
Master,

00:11:11.500 --> 00:11:13.160
Miss Shei requests to see you.

00:11:31.850 --> 00:11:33.540
Now that you're in the city,

00:11:34.510 --> 00:11:36.510
why not just visit Sword King Manor?

00:11:37.150 --> 00:11:38.610
No need to visit in person.

00:11:39.920 --> 00:11:41.720
The bigger the stir I made today,

00:11:42.670 --> 00:11:44.200
the more attention I'd draw

00:11:44.780 --> 00:11:45.780
to myself.

00:11:46.630 --> 00:11:48.490
You don't just want the attention

00:11:48.890 --> 00:11:50.220
of Sword King Yu, right?

00:11:51.430 --> 00:11:52.360
Since I've come,

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:54.970
he'll definitely come too.

00:11:58.150 --> 00:11:58.870
What's going on?

00:11:58.870 --> 00:12:00.030
Yeah, it's so cold.

00:12:01.400 --> 00:12:02.320
It suddenly got cold.

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:03.390
Indeed.

00:12:05.030 --> 00:12:06.270
Why did it suddenly get cold?

00:12:06.270 --> 00:12:06.910
Yeah.

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:08.000
It's snowing.

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:13.240
It's snowing.

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:14.440
I'm Xue Xianzi.

00:12:14.750 --> 00:12:16.510
I've long heard of your name, Sword King.

00:12:16.510 --> 00:12:18.170
Please give me some guidance.

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:25.320
Xue Xianzi?

00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:29.790
Is that really Xue Xianzi?

00:12:29.790 --> 00:12:30.790
Is it an impostor?

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:32.320
He's acting mysteriously.

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:33.580
He must be an impostor.

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:35.800
What a surprise.

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:38.500
Xue Xianzi,
the Hermit of Snow, has come too.

00:12:39.030 --> 00:12:40.630
You're a master of the sword.

00:12:40.960 --> 00:12:42.090
I don't dare presume

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:45.500
to offer any guidance.

00:12:58.530 --> 00:12:59.150
I can't say

00:13:00.710 --> 00:13:02.280
you are wrong.

00:13:17.870 --> 00:13:19.630
You flatter me, Sword King.

00:13:20.390 --> 00:13:21.890
The Yu family has produced
ten generations of Sword Kings,

00:13:21.890 --> 00:13:23.240
while I've only been known

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:25.240
for a few short decades.

00:13:25.670 --> 00:13:26.870
How could my pale snow

00:13:26.920 --> 00:13:29.190
ever compare to your blazing flame?

00:13:29.860 --> 00:13:30.790
How arrogant!

00:13:31.270 --> 00:13:31.910
Is he…

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:34.390
truly Xue Xianzi?

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:35.610
I've met him before—

00:13:35.790 --> 00:13:36.550
once in the jianghu

00:13:36.550 --> 00:13:37.720
with my senior.

00:13:38.630 --> 00:13:39.320
That is

00:13:39.950 --> 00:13:40.670
indeed him.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:43.720
Please,

00:13:43.720 --> 00:13:45.240
do me the honor.

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:47.000
You flatter me.

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.870
We both share a love for swordsmanship.

00:13:49.870 --> 00:13:50.600
A friendly match

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:51.630
is all.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:53.510
Please.

00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:54.750
Then, Sword King,

00:13:54.910 --> 00:13:56.480
prepare yourself

00:13:56.480 --> 00:13:57.410
for this strike.

00:14:08.150 --> 00:14:09.270
The Hermit of Snow.

00:14:10.040 --> 00:14:10.970
It really is him.

00:14:17.130 --> 00:14:18.770
Sword King, let's see if you

00:14:18.800 --> 00:14:20.270
can withstand this strike

00:14:20.270 --> 00:14:21.080
from me.

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:09.440
It seems

00:15:09.940 --> 00:15:11.140
everyone has seen

00:15:11.520 --> 00:15:14.050
Sword King Yu's
Westwind Slashing Wildfire.

00:15:22.110 --> 00:15:23.040
Are you alright?

00:15:31.820 --> 00:15:32.600
Oh, no.

00:15:44.270 --> 00:15:44.840
He lost.

00:15:45.630 --> 00:15:46.090
He lost?

00:15:47.250 --> 00:15:48.310
What's happening?

00:15:49.790 --> 00:15:50.590
You really are

00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:52.550
the top swordsman of our time—

00:15:52.550 --> 00:15:54.010
Yu Qifeng, the Sword King.

00:15:54.240 --> 00:15:54.790
I've

00:15:55.840 --> 00:15:56.270
lost.

00:16:02.910 --> 00:16:04.110
Looks like Xue Xianzi

00:16:04.320 --> 00:16:05.780
is here to stir up trouble.

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:12.520
Yu Qifeng's Westwind Slashing Wildfire

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:14.530
truly lives up to its reputation.

00:16:14.990 --> 00:16:15.700
I am

00:16:15.720 --> 00:16:16.890
so impressed.

00:16:19.410 --> 00:16:21.070
Westwind Slashing Wildfire?

00:16:31.530 --> 00:16:33.400
Miss Shei, please go inside first.

00:16:33.400 --> 00:16:35.200
I have some matters to attend to.

00:16:36.260 --> 00:16:37.390
All right, Mr. Tang.

00:16:43.120 --> 00:16:43.670
Shen.

00:16:48.510 --> 00:16:49.510
It's time.

00:16:50.150 --> 00:16:50.680
Let's go.

00:16:54.930 --> 00:17:00.070
[Tianyan Sword Wall, Sword King City]

00:17:05.349 --> 00:17:06.510
Tianyan Sword Wall.

00:17:07.710 --> 00:17:09.910
So this is Yu Xuanqing's sword essence.

00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:11.680
It's truly powerful.

00:17:12.640 --> 00:17:13.510
What a pity.

00:17:14.349 --> 00:17:15.880
This secret legacy exists,

00:17:16.579 --> 00:17:18.440
yet there's no worthy successor.

00:17:18.640 --> 00:17:20.040
The grand Sword King City

00:17:20.680 --> 00:17:22.410
has long been blinded by greed.

00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:23.680
Otherwise,

00:17:24.200 --> 00:17:25.240
how could it have been tainted

00:17:25.240 --> 00:17:26.640
by the Blood Ghost Pills?

00:17:26.920 --> 00:17:28.109
Why did you

00:17:29.590 --> 00:17:30.390
bring me here?

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:32.330
To rattle the grass…

00:17:34.120 --> 00:17:35.450
and scare out the snake.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:14.200
There's indeed more to it than it seems.

00:19:26.910 --> 00:19:28.770
The essence of the Sword Phoenix?

00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:42.890
You are not of this realm.

00:19:43.610 --> 00:19:45.540
Why have you set foot in this realm?

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:48.800
Only when one abandons the mortal flesh

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:51.130
and comes between reality and the void

00:19:51.860 --> 00:19:54.060
can one glimpse the past and the future.

00:19:56.960 --> 00:19:58.280
I am Tang Lici.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:01.480
Please grant me your guidance,
Sword Phoenix.

00:20:07.370 --> 00:20:08.710
A golden eye on the forehead…

00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:09.920
Yique Yinyang,

00:20:10.170 --> 00:20:11.140
it's you.

00:20:12.760 --> 00:20:14.420
You're actually still alive.

00:20:15.050 --> 00:20:16.310
Since that's the case,

00:20:19.620 --> 00:20:21.770
I shall take your life here!

00:20:49.600 --> 00:20:50.720
Such power…

00:20:51.260 --> 00:20:53.520
That's the Westwind Slashing Wildfire.

00:20:53.640 --> 00:20:55.300
Westwind Slashing Wildfire?

00:20:56.030 --> 00:20:56.720
But

00:20:57.430 --> 00:20:59.060
why is it different from the one

00:20:59.060 --> 00:21:01.060
Sword King Yu unleashed earlier?

00:21:01.400 --> 00:21:02.550
Yeah, it looks different.

00:21:02.550 --> 00:21:03.310
What's going on?

00:21:03.310 --> 00:21:04.070
Indeed.

00:21:04.960 --> 00:21:07.440
Sword King Yu's sword essence
is as dark as night.

00:21:07.440 --> 00:21:09.000
Why is this one crimson red?

