00:28:32.610 --> 00:28:34.000
the one who captured Jiang Qingyu

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:34.960
was me.

00:28:35.790 --> 00:28:37.120
Tang Lici captured him?

00:28:37.450 --> 00:28:37.920
What?

00:28:38.270 --> 00:28:39.240
Didn't Sword King Yu say

00:28:39.240 --> 00:28:40.310
that he personally captured

00:28:40.310 --> 00:28:41.110
Jiang Qingyu?

00:28:41.880 --> 00:28:42.350
Second,

00:28:43.850 --> 00:28:45.030
Jiang Qingyu was involved

00:28:45.030 --> 00:28:46.530
in the Hao family massacre.

