Mr. Tang,

00:28:52.330 --> 00:28:54.930
are you doubting my ability
to handle the case?

00:28:55.240 --> 00:28:56.520
I have my own leads,

00:28:56.990 --> 00:28:58.600
but one person's judgment alone

00:28:58.600 --> 00:29:00.060
can't convince everyone.

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:01.930
Then Sword King,

00:29:02.640 --> 00:29:05.100
why not hold a public trial
for Jiang Qingyu?

00:29:06.310 --> 00:29:07.440
Yes, a public trial.

00:29:07.440 --> 00:29:08.970
Yes, a public trial!

00:29:09.270 --> 00:29:10.440
Since the Master of Wanqiao Chamber

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:11.770
is involved in the case,

00:29:11.880 --> 00:29:13.200
a public trial is the only way
to convince everyone.

00:29:13.200 --> 00:29:14.440
Yes, bring Jiang Qingyu to trial!

00:29:14.440 --> 00:29:14.920
Public trial!

00:29:14.920 --> 00:29:15.920
Try him publicly!

00:29:15.960 --> 00:29:17.070
That's right.

00:29:17.070 --> 00:29:17.870
Public trial!

00:29:18.110 --> 00:29:18.720
Public trial!

00:29:18.720 --> 00:29:19.160
Public trial!

00:29:19.160 --> 00:29:20.350
Put Jiang Qingyu on public trial.

