You're all correct.

00:29:22.590 --> 00:29:23.310
He should be

00:29:23.310 --> 00:29:24.880
interrogated in front of

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:26.320
all martial artists.

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:28.110
It seems

00:29:28.790 --> 00:29:30.480
I've arrived at the perfect time.

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:31.830
Those with purpose

00:29:32.370 --> 00:29:34.170
always arrive at the right time.

