At the Qiongtai Banquet
the day after tomorrow,

00:29:40.030 --> 00:29:41.830
I will publicly try Jiang Qingyu

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:43.410
and give the martial arts world

00:29:43.410 --> 00:29:44.850
a satisfactory answer.

