Anyone in Sword King City
is welcome to attend.

00:29:47.640 --> 00:29:48.840
Let's try him together

00:29:48.840 --> 00:29:50.830
and expose the mastermind behind him!

00:29:50.830 --> 00:29:52.270
-Great!
-Great!

00:29:53.720 --> 00:29:55.160
The Sword King is wise!

00:29:55.160 --> 00:29:59.200
The Sword King is wise!

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:00.550
Mr. Tang,

00:30:01.750 --> 00:30:02.830
do you dare to come?

00:30:03.840 --> 00:30:05.170
If the Sword King dares,

00:30:07.810 --> 00:30:09.130
why wouldn't I?

00:31:56.410 --> 00:31:57.610
As a small punishment

00:31:58.300 --> 00:31:59.360
for arriving late,

00:32:01.280 --> 00:32:01.880
my friend.

00:32:35.440 --> 00:32:37.040
The drizzle's just stopped.

00:32:37.240 --> 00:32:38.580
The monk is tired of the journey.

00:32:38.580 --> 00:32:40.510
The Go game is like the game of stars.

00:32:40.510 --> 00:32:42.120
You always sought solitude.

00:32:42.890 --> 00:32:43.750
I never thought

00:32:43.950 --> 00:32:46.080
you'd be disturbed by worldly affairs

00:32:46.900 --> 00:32:48.110
and go to Sword King City

00:32:48.110 --> 00:32:49.710
for the Sword Duel Festival.

00:32:51.360 --> 00:32:53.090
I'm no man of the mundane world.

00:32:53.640 --> 00:32:54.770
With no attachments

00:32:54.920 --> 00:32:55.720
or obstacles,

00:32:56.400 --> 00:32:57.730
I come and go as I please.

00:32:58.970 --> 00:33:01.100
You've been pondering for a long time.

00:33:02.260 --> 00:33:03.860
Something's troubling you?

00:33:19.880 --> 00:33:20.830
Three years ago,

00:33:21.700 --> 00:33:23.840
we played our first game
at Wenqi Pavilion.

00:33:23.840 --> 00:33:24.600
Since then,

00:33:25.070 --> 00:33:26.070
we've bonded through Go,

00:33:26.070 --> 00:33:27.200
meeting once a year.

00:33:28.110 --> 00:33:29.640
Though I call you my friend,

00:33:31.240 --> 00:33:33.100
I've never truly understood you.

00:33:47.350 --> 00:33:48.400
The path you seek

00:33:49.110 --> 00:33:50.510
is the path of salvation.

