00:36:49.630 --> 00:36:51.560
Tang Lici is
the Master of Wanqiao Chamber?

00:36:51.560 --> 00:36:52.280
That brat

00:36:52.280 --> 00:36:54.550
just seized
the Sword Phoenix's essence
just like that

00:36:54.550 --> 00:36:55.950
